{"tid":2097284,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人係「中國人」","createTime":"2020-07-06T16:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T02:40:25.000Z","uid":22001,"like":16,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"11fdf2ad5ae8068089683b4b6d4ea72b7fa5eed5","tid":2097284,"uid":22001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:20:27.000Z","msg":"老一輩多數都係大中華膠<br />\n所以先會有涂謹申呢類人自認中國人<br />\n但係屌佢地之前，都應該要理解下佢地點解有咁既諗法<br />\n<br />\n早排同呀爺嘈，講到底台灣人香港人係咪中國人<br />\n我就梗係話基於文化同理念，就梗係唔係<br />\n佢聽到就發哂老脾話香港人同台灣人都係由中國移居<br />\n<br />\n我再問，咁咩叫「中國」<br />\n佢話中國係一個概念，係一個群體（留意返，佢唔係用國家既concept）<br />\n<br />\n我再問，咁中國係咪等於中共<br />\n佢一聽到就好大反應話「唔係，只係當年中華民國退守大陸，先會俾中共夾硬搶咗中國呢個名黎用」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知係咪每個老一輩既都係咁諗<br />\n但就咁聽落，佢地認同自己係中國人，只係因為佢地係嗰個群體出身，但唔代表佢地認同中共<br />\n佢地心目中一樣係唔憤氣中共騎劫咗中國人呢個concept<br />\n<br />\n如果想擴大黃圈，一定要了解唔同背景既人對唔同concept既definition<br />\n明咗之後，分分鐘其實大家講緊同一個不滿"},{"pid":"3cc752fa02a9a1b8156ba04f2bddb7315714dd49","tid":2097284,"uid":107842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"你個Title -,-"},{"pid":"e14d99da7bee5f81e394bbc1f52d47c8737a8709","tid":2097284,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"tldr"},{"pid":"aeb3972ae7fa094d65faef4375b0e1b50f991c14","tid":2097284,"uid":301989,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦 大支那膠死全家 一票不頭廢土 廢土死全黨"},{"pid":"19e6449a7b3ff1622540a2853e4b1bb77beab4f7","tid":2097284,"uid":22001,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:25:54.000Z","msg":"切身啲講 <br />\n如果有一日香港走淨班新移民同藍絲，自稱真香港人，我地都唔會轉口否定自己係香港人呢個身份<br />\n<br />\n因為就算我地走去邊都好，我地都係講法治講民本講廣東話既香港出世同成長，而我地都認同呢一套理念<br />\n所以我地先係真既香港人"},{"pid":"e082b94f3dadba146ad516d8eeee95f838f4bfac","tid":2097284,"uid":161726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"香港人係「中國人」，然後藍屍大大聲話你係曱甴。"},{"pid":"ab86adb2982ecd13aa110a4d45671d3604947c8f","tid":2097284,"uid":22001,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"3cc752fa02a9a1b8156ba04f2bddb7315714dd49","tid":2097284,"uid":107842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"你個Title -,-"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:26:22.000Z","msg":"Sor,標題撚"},{"pid":"183bccb050f808c3710b51ad6c899083932d0b25","tid":2097284,"uid":22001,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"aeb3972ae7fa094d65faef4375b0e1b50f991c14","tid":2097284,"uid":301989,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦 大支那膠死全家 一票不頭廢土 廢土死全黨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:29:23.000Z","msg":"唔係為民主派平反，但如果你想拉攏更多老一輩變黃，就要明白佢地先"},{"pid":"62020bb32cf5f5188816002d44e510ae2a088c69","tid":2097284,"uid":22001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e14d99da7bee5f81e394bbc1f52d47c8737a8709","tid":2097284,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"tldr"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd9bf9d3d85e0a265bd1130f5a1053fc959eaec","tid":2097284,"uid":35420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:31:04.000Z","msg":"NMSL"},{"pid":"4eec82cb0c1210d7a54aac0c62f6fe692fb71d16","tid":2097284,"uid":22001,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T16:32:13.000Z","msg":"避免返誤會  我到而家都唔認同自己係中國人<br />\n但當你改變唔到老一輩既身分認同，令佢地認清黨=/=國係其中一個做法"},{"pid":"f01e26942da57090d816b38812c2d25b0a190bdf","tid":2097284,"uid":22001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bdd9bf9d3d85e0a265bd1130f5a1053fc959eaec","tid":2097284,"uid":35420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20